<p>Nice hat.<img src="/assets/images/2013/12/PC123575.jpg" alt="OLYMPUS DIGITAL CAMERA" /></p>

<p>This is Clear Water Temple itself, with a view of Kyoto in the background. Built in 1633, it is a magnificent piece of carpentry.</p>

<p><a href="http://phwl.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/PC123664.jpg"><img src="http://phwl.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/PC123664.jpg" alt="" class="align-center" /></a></p>

<p>Massive pieces of timber were used and lots of fancy joints.</p>

<p><a href="http://phwl.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/PC123590.jpg"><img src="http://phwl.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/PC123590.jpg" alt="" class="align-center" /></a></p>

<p>This picture is actually quite misleading as autumn was long over.<a href="http://phwl.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/PC123671.jpg"><img src="http://phwl.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/PC123671.jpg" alt="" class="align-center" /></a></p>

