<p>Japanese marbled beef restaurant.</p>

<p><a href="http://phwl.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/PC123809.jpg"><img src="http://phwl.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/PC123809.jpg" alt="" class="align-center" /></a></p>

<p>The Shinto Fushimi Inari Shrine with many torii gates.</p>

<p><a href="http://www.phwl.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/PC123748.jpg"><img src="http://www.phwl.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/PC123748.jpg" alt="" class="align-center" /></a></p>

<p>Of all the places we visited, I was most impressed by Nijo Castle and its surrounding gardens.</p>

<p><a href="http://www.phwl.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/PC133982.jpg"><img src="http://www.phwl.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/PC133982.jpg" alt="" class="align-center" /></a></p>

